reviewText: I would be happy to pay $50. I can't do the $150. I was trying to get this before they stop selling it with no luck. This band does RULE!

I've seen a lot of bands in my time; I have never experienced a band like this one.  I believe there will never be no other band that will top this one's acts.  This dvd is beyond anything I ever experienced.  Just as Jimi would have said, ARE YOU EXPERIENCED? If you think that you can handle this dvd go for it, If not stay away. XXX
